How to update escape limits

1. Select file
2. Select Set escape distance
3. Enter escape distance
4. It should reject anything you put in that isn't an int greater than or equal to 1

How to update escape time
1. Select file
2. Select Set escape time
3. Enter escape time 
4. It should reject anything you put in that isn't an int greater than or equal to 1 or less than or equal to 255